```plantuml
@startuml Sanperolo_The-Intelligent-Bike

actor User
participant "Sensors" as Sensors
participant "MQTT Broker" as MQTT
participant "Backend Server" as Backend
database "SQL Database" as Database
participant "Frontend Dashboard" as Frontend
participant "Node.js Server" as NodeServer

User -> Frontend: Access Dashboard
Frontend -> NodeServer: Request Web Application
NodeServer -> Frontend: Deliver Angular App

Sensors -> MQTT: Publish Sensor Data
MQTT -> Backend: Forward Sensor Data
Backend -> Database: Store Sensor Data

Frontend -> Backend: Request Sensor Data
Backend -> Database: Query Sensor Data
Database -> Backend: Return Sensor Data
Backend -> Frontend: Deliver Sensor Data

@enduml
```